parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering assist system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The steering wheel jerks or slips to one side
the vehicle wanders or pulls to one side
loss of steering control
oversteering
and sudden changes in steering resistance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake failure due to corrosion of brake lines can cause loss of brake function, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
brake failure
ABS activation
and corrosion of brake lines.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: ABS system failure can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, or near-misses, especially at low speeds.
symptoms: ABS system activates at low speeds
brake pedal pulsates
and increased stopping distance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake master cylinder failure can cause loss of brake function, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal goes to the floor
and brake failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rotor Warping and Brake Pad Wear
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rotor warping and brake pad wear can cause loss of brake function, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Rotors warp
brake pads wear out quickly
and brake failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wiper motor can cause reduced visibility during rainy or snowy conditions, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Windshield wipers work intermittently or not at all
wipers stop in any position
wipers come on and off on their own
humming noise from the wiper motor when turned on
wipers may work for a short time and then quit.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle jerks or lunges forward
the transmission makes a loud whining or grinding noise
the vehicle will not shift into gear
the vehicle will not reverse
the transmission leaks fluid.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sun gear shell can cause the transmission to fail, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission makes a loud whining or grinding noise
the vehicle will not shift into gear
the vehicle will not reverse
the transmission leaks fluid.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the reverse drum can cause the transmission to fail, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle will not shift into reverse
the transmission makes a loud whining or grinding noise
the transmission leaks fluid.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the brake ABS system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The ABS system activates at every stop
the speed sensors have been replaced multiple times.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shift interlock can cause the vehicle to move unexpectedly, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle can be shifted into gear without depressing the brake pedal
the vehicle can move unexpectedly.
